episodes.title: WE NEED YOUR HELP! Parliamentary Inquiry into CULTS #Scientology #Advocacy #Cult #news
episodes.description:
https://www.parliament.vic.gov.au/cofg

INQUIRY into the RECRUITMENT METHODS and IMPACTS of CULTS and organised fringe groups https://www.parliament.vic.gov.au/cofg. EVERYONE IS WELCOME! LET'S DO THIS TOGETHER!!


The Parliament of Victoria has launched an Inquiry into the recruitment methods and impacts of cults and organised fringe groups, which is open for submissions until 31 JULY 2025. If you or anyone you know has been involved with a cult that has a presence in Victoria, Australia, you're highly encouraged to make a submission. There’s also an anonymous questionnaire option available for those who might not wish to make a full submission. https://www.parliament.vic.gov.au/cofg

If you'd like some help doing yours you can reach out to Stop Religious Coercion at:

Website: http://stopreligiouscoercision.au/
Facebook group: https://www.facebook.com/groups/1265536041331385
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@stop_religious_coercion
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/stop.religiouscoercionau/
